## Portfolio Website

This is a **Next.js portfolio website** for a fullstack developer transitioning to freelancing. The project showcases technical skills through:

**Key Features:**

- Interactive visual components (e.g., Planets.tsx - a physics-based solar system simulation using p5.js)
- Internationalization support (English/Ukrainian)
- TypeScript + SCSS modules
- Material-UI components

**Tech Stack:** Next.js, TypeScript, React, SCSS, p5.js, MUI, SQL

**Purpose:** Demonstrate technical expertise and creative problem-solving to attract freelance clients through engaging interactive experiences and clean, professional presentation.
